HEADWORD: Centropomus
<hw>Centropomus</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>the type genus of the
<fam>Centropomidae</fam>, comprising the <er>snooks</er>, and including
<spn>Centropomus undecimalis</spn>, a large bony sport fish also
esteemed as food.</def>⟦br⟧
